%r
mean <- colMeans(Subject_2020, na.rm = TRUE)
mean_score <- c()
for (i in mean){
    mean_score <- append(mean_score, i)
}
mean_score <- round(mean_score, digits = 2)

average_score <- data.frame(subject, mean_score)

%r
mean_score_subject_2020 <- ggplot(average_score, aes(x=subject, y=mean_score, fill=subject)) + 
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  geom_text(aes(label = round(mean_score, 1)), vjust = -0.3, size = 4) +
  labs(title="Diem trung binh mon hoc 2020",
       x ="Mon Hoc", y = "Diem trung binh")
